  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/45ae7a6ed6348142a06390426d06bab9.poster.avif?t=1728554862\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/45ae7a6ed6348142a06390426d06bab9.webm?t=1728554862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/45ae7a6ed6348142a06390426d06bab9.mp4?t=1728554862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Loop</h2></strong>Explore a dynamic world where each loop brings new challenges.</li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic Turn-Based Combat</h2></strong>Engage glitch-infested foes with tactical precision.</li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the Art of Parrying</h2></strong> Employ a unique, accessible yet challenging parry system crucial for success in combat. Inspired by games like Dark Souls, Sekiro, and Nioh, but designed for a turn-based format.</li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgradable Arsenal</h2></strong>Customize your robotic abilities to conquer the ever-changing digital landscape.</li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Neon Aesthetics</h2></strong>Immerse yourself in a visually stunning cybernetic realm.</li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/d5e25f190efb43f71d3949bb3dbcdfad.poster.avif?t=1728554862\" width=614 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/d5e25f190efb43f71d3949bb3dbcdfad.webm?t=1728554862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564350/extras/d5e25f190efb43f71d3949bb3dbcdfad.mp4?t=1728554862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p>",
